<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITexelArrayOutput.GetOptimalDataFormat" Title="GetOptimalDataFormat method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITexelArrayOutput">ITexelArrayOutput</PageRef> ->
    GetOptimalDataFormat
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>GetOptimalDataFormat</TypeRef> method returns the SourceDataFormat that most closely matches the format of the captured texel data.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[ITexelArray::SourceDataFormat GetOptimalDataFormat() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="ITexelArray::SourceDataFormat">
        The source data format that can read the captured output without unnecessary conversion.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
